title: Camco RhinoFLEX RV Wye Sewer Hose Fitting with 360 Degree Swivel Ends | Allows for Two Sewer Hoses to Connect to the Same Dump Station | Ideal for Motorhomes (39812), Orange
description: Camco's RhinoFLEX RV Wye allows two sewer hoses with lug fittings to be connected to the same dump station. It has built-in gaskets for odor tight connections. Two ends have bayonet fittings and one end has a lug fitting. All three ends swivel 360 degrees for ease of use.
